6:
Ahaha... AHAHAHA! Finally, a REAL 
threat! I was startin' to think this place 
was for babies!
11:
Goin' for the kill? Sorry, but you're 
gonna have to try WAY harder than 
that!
16:
DAHAHAHA! Now THAT'S what I'm talkin 
about, baby! Only one of us is makin' it 
out alive. Question is, who's it gonna 
be?
18:
Get ready to meet your maker, 
and tell 'em who sent ya!
28:
Apologies, Gilasrad, but you have to 
understand—these policies are in 
place for your protection. We cannot 
offer such a treacherous quest to just 
a single person!
31:
*sigh* We really doing this same song 
and dance again? How many times 
have I put myself on the line for the 
guild now?
34:
I-I'm afraid I'm going to have to put 
my foot down this time—I can't handle 
the stress of waiting for you to come 
back every time!
37:
If I die, I die, right? That's the risk that 
we ALL take as adventurers. Let's not 
beat around the bush here.
40:
G-Guild orders! You are NOT to go on 
that quest on your own. Um... Alk here 
will accompany you!
46:
Y-yes! Please. If another adventurer 
dies under my watch, I'll be demoted 
for sure!
48:
You won't let that happen to me—er, 
Gilasrad, now, would you? Please, oh, 
please!
I swear... He's gonna give me an ulcer 
one of these days.
51: Sorry about all the fuss, kid.
54:
Oh, no. It's fine. What's your deal, 
anyway?
58:
Me? I'm nobody. Just a guy lookin' to 
have some fun!
62:
Looks like we've got company. Let's 
move!
67:
Ahaha! Here we go! This one's 
bloodthirsty!
78:
Are you crazy?! You could've gotten 
yourself killed there!
83:
Hahaha! Not bad, kid! That beast 
wasn't quite good enough, but 
a decent warm-up nonetheless!
85:
I just gotta FEEL the heat of battle to 
get my fix of adventure, you know? 
It ain't a real one without a thrill!
87:
I've lost count of how many near-
death escapes I've had. That's why 
they call me the Deathrush Berserker!
94:
Hey, sorry for the trouble. You can 
have the lion's share of the reward for 
finishing it off.
97: Nah, I'm fine with going halfsies.
100:
And I don't think the fact that you've 
survived for so long isn't just a happy 
accident—you've got talent.
105:
Heh! Appreciate the recognition. What 
do you say we celebrate with an ice-
cold—
113:
...I'll handle our star attraction. You 
good with taking on the sideshows?
121: Heh! I'll show you, all right.
125:
But this ain't just a game... 
One slipup could be fatal.
128:
Yet for some reason... I can't stop 
smilin'!
137:
Geez, you actually took it down all on 
your own!
141:
I can't take all the credit. It was thanks 
to you I was able to focus on the big 
guy.
144:
I should probably lay low for a while, 
though. The guild's probably had it up 
to here with me, ya know?
154:
HAHAHAHA! No way! You're tellin' me 
this is another world entirely?
161:
Like it? It's the ultimate thrill-seeker's 
paradise!
164:
Better than hiding out in any cave, 
that's for sure!
